So, let's make the world a better place by doing happiness hunting TOGETHER. Wanna be strong and powerful? Then lift someone up.

caption.text: #jogja #malioboro #nomnom #smile #selfie

To wake up on a gloriously bright and cold morning
in a tent we made before
pitched beneath spruce trees

And to look out for a moment
from the open side of the tent
across the dead camp-fire of the night before
Lazily and sleepily
like a larva in a pupa

To hear the birds' songs
and the crickets' songs
of the joy of the wild
As the sun goes up and rises
gliding through the cloud

Or to wake at night
when we have rolled in our sleeping bags
feel the frosty air, feel the backache
and give each other a big happy smile

To look up through the leaves above to the dark sky
and meet the wonderful moon and flashing stars

Sawiran, October 22-24, 2014
